{"tid":533810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得對牙朗太差後悔了唔反佢","createTime":"2018-01-19T07:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T19:51:13.000Z","uid":130419,"like":46,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0ba7c460fc4bc6b99091ba5339ba5efdec10e0fd","tid":533810,"uid":130419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/153232_6623a8e689614da0280aad7f1f3cb76f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F153232_6623a8e689614da0280aad7f1f3cb76f.png&h=45e26482&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/153241_1d425edeeaced13815fcec37ed7935a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F153241_1d425edeeaced13815fcec37ed7935a4.png&h=088b38e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/153257_a2ef1d730a05f58bed6657586cbe0b35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F153257_a2ef1d730a05f58bed6657586cbe0b35.png&h=4e6e2c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你連登啲反朗都係抽下水姐<br />\n人地黃金生涯比晒你 <br />\n皇馬迷就叫佢退役又叫佢走 慘過地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近年就吹奏施丹 依家差啲就屌到佢一文不值<br />\n遠啲屌到卡斯拿斯走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n覺得佢好慘 唔反住了<br />\n將呢個任務留返比皇馬球迷了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n留名睇人拖美斯巴塞落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好屌到人變地底泥由皇馬迷講特別有說服力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔反朗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7520d50adbe40ebacf8c6badcff013c1f927aba","tid":533810,"uid":33601,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/154321_dfe5e0ec5b1e104c643f90a9794dc684.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F154321_dfe5e0ec5b1e104c643f90a9794dc684.gif&h=2b1b2cd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d910cd7c3c6ecaa90c3055dc8af9fafc12900d7","tid":533810,"uid":130419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:44:15.000Z","msg":"希望馬迷大方啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔好逼c朗走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3496b90e0f438e8b14322dd18e73a915de4c84fd","tid":533810,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da65ca3f08d17f905c0f211f81ff1d468d5f6aa","tid":533810,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7520d50adbe40ebacf8c6badcff013c1f927aba","tid":533810,"uid":33601,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:43:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/19/154321_dfe5e0ec5b1e104c643f90a9794dc684.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F19%2F154321_dfe5e0ec5b1e104c643f90a9794dc684.gif&h=2b1b2cd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T07:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\